1
00:00:00,619 --> 00:00:06,444
UNK

2
00:00:09,985 --> 00:00:16,543
un in Ponevezher lager, khotsh mir zaynen dortn geven a kurtse tsayt, oyf vifl ikh gedenk,

3
00:00:16,633 --> 00:00:25,149
inem in dem grupe iz er geven dort Shmerke Spivak, mayner a khaver, velkher ikh hob zikh mit im bakent in geto, un er iz arayngefaln tsuzamen mit mir in Ponevezher lager.

4
00:00:25,780 --> 00:00:31,916
Shmerke Spivok iz geven a a yat aza min volt ikh gezogn mer a hendler vi kemfer.

5
00:00:32,395 --> 00:00:39,628
nor in undzer organiz- in undzer krayzl hot er azoy gepast, vayl er iz geven a dreyster yat, er hot keyn nit moyre gehat far keyn far keyn far rizikalishe arbet.

6
00:00:39,938 --> 00:00:45,478
un mir hobn im gegebn a oyfgabe tsu krign farbindungen mit di u- mit di

7
00:00:45,478 --> 00:00:48,473
rusishe plenikes velkhe flegn kumen arbetn oyfn erodrom,

8
00:00:48,473 --> 00:00:52,689
efsher mit zey zikh vos tsu derredn, far zey UNK tsu gefinen

9
00:00:52,898 --> 00:00:59,307
derredn tsu gefinen a opsh- a a a a a shprakh

10
00:00:59,307 --> 00:01:03,185
vi azoy tsu, efsher veysn zey vu es gefinen zikh partizaner arum Ponevezh.

11
00:01:03,765 --> 00:01:07,928
Shmerke Spivok hot zikh hot gekent gut rusish,

12
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:16,925
un er hot zikh prubirt mit im tsunoyf reydn mi- mit di pleni- mit di plenikes mit mitn brigadir fun di plenikes, vayl der brigadir iz geven UNK mer veyniker azoy tsu zogn

13
00:01:16,925 --> 00:01:21,647
a solider mentsh, a solider soldat, er iz gevezn a soldat, oder a ofitsir,

14
00:01:24,218 --> 00:01:30,641
un di, hot zikh aroysgevizn az bay di plenikes iz shoyn oykh geven a u- um- umlegale organizatsye, zey hobn oykh getrakht a- antloyfn.

15
00:01:31,356 --> 00:01:35,720
un tsu- un zey hobn undz tsugezogt az zey veln baym antloyfn veln zey undz gebn a signal

16
00:01:35,811 --> 00:01:37,729
un mir zoln loyfn mit zey tsuzamen.

17
00:01:40,249 --> 00:01:44,647
nokhn, mir hobn zikh zeyer opgeredt mit im, mit dem brigadir zeyern,

18
00:01:44,890 --> 00:01:50,422
in a tog, az mir veln zikh trefn un er vet undz zogn, gebn a karte

19
00:01:50,422 --> 00:01:54,874
un vayzn vu gefinen zikh partizaner, vayl bay zey iz shoyn geven tsugegreyt a karte.

20
00:01:57,985 --> 00:02:07,699
grod oyf morgn iz er shoyn nit iz hot men di brigade hot men di di arbeter brigade fun di plenikes nit ge- nit gekumen nit getribn tsu der arbet dortn un er mir hobn farloyrn di farbindungen in gantsn mit im.

21
00:02:07,823 --> 00:02:16,794
hobn mir bashlosn aroystsulozn in di hinter shtot, in der in der Ponevezh iz geven a hobn mir a- iz geven a derfl,

22
00:02:18,775 --> 00:02:25,384
vu mir hobn gehert fun di fun farsheydene arbeter velkhe hobn gearbet oyfn erodrom az dortn bavayzn zikh oft mol oft mol partizaner.

23
00:02:25,997 --> 00:02:32,218
hobn mir gehat aroysgelozn undzerer a y- a yungn yatl, fun a yor tsvelf tsi elf iz er geven. zayn familye gedenk ikh shoyn nit.

24
00:02:32,477 --> 00:02:36,709
a dreyster yat, mir hobn gegebn im instruktsyes vi azoy tsum firn zikh,

25
00:02:36,709 --> 00:02:41,735
un er iz avekgelofn, fun der arbet iz iz er hot er zikh aroysgeganvet un antlofn in dorf,

26
00:02:43,362 --> 00:02:48,688
un dortn hot er, tsu tsu dervisn zikh ven es kumen dortn di partizaner, kedey mit zey tsu krign a far- kontakt,

27
00:02:49,757 --> 00:02:55,066
aroystsu- aroystsu- tsu antloyfn fun dortn. etlekhe mol iz geven der der yatl,

28
00:02:56,102 --> 00:02:58,698
un er hot shoyn gehat mit zey gehat er hot gehat tsugeredt opgeredt

29
00:02:58,698 --> 00:03:03,221
vi azoy zey veln undz oyf- vi azoy zey viln, zey hobn zikh oykh oykh gevolt trefn mit undz,

30
00:03:03,221 --> 00:03:05,799
mir hobn zey mir mir hobn zey gezogt mir hobn

31
00:03:06,278 --> 00:03:11,216
a eyn pistolet in gantsn, un a raketnik iz bay undz geven, a raketnik,

32
00:03:11,256 --> 00:03:13,798
vos ikh hob gefunen oyfn arbetndik oyf erodrom.

33
00:03:14,243 --> 00:03:24,109
dos iz geven optsu- optsush- optsushrekn efsher a mol mer nit di di vikh- ve- velkhe di velkhe farshteyen nit vos nit iz oyfn veg, oyb oyfn veg tsu di partizaner.

34
00:03:26,967 --> 00:03:31,736
hot der yingl, mit dem UNK, ikh muz zogn vegn dem tragishn toyt fun dem yingl.

35
00:03:32,383 --> 00:03:35,650
dem yingl hot men, ven m'hot undz gebrakht shpeter in Shtuthof,

36
00:03:37,851 --> 00:03:41,102
iz der yingl aroysgegangen fun vagon,

37
00:03:42,087 --> 00:03:49,117
un er iz aru- aruntergefaln unter vagon un der vagon un der di reder fun vagon hobn im opgeshnitn beyde fis.

38
00:03:49,528 --> 00:03:58,585
ikh bin tsugelofn a kuk ton, er iz gelegn, der yingl, blas in gantsn, vays, on fis.

39
00:03:59,940 --> 00:04:01,650
ikh hob poshet nit gekent oyshaltn.

40
00:04:01,650 --> 00:04:06,465
aza min yunger kind, vos hot azoy fil geholfn, un er hot gehat aza min sof.

41
00:04:07,281 --> 00:04:09,536
nu ikh vil zikh itster umkern tsurik vegn Ponevezh.

42
00:04:13,373 --> 00:04:22,445
un UNK vartndik DA, ya unter, s'geven der der in Ponevezh iz geven der brigadir fun undzer brigade fun erodrom iz geven eyner

43
00:04:22,603 --> 00:04:28,065
Solomon Mil. dos iz geven a barimter inzhenier fun Kovne

44
00:04:28,645 --> 00:04:31,519
velkher hot gestroyet dortn, velkher hot geboyt dortn di garazhn,

45
00:04:31,519 --> 00:04:37,718
dem barimtn garazh fun Kovne, velkher hot geboyt groyse obyektn in Kovne. er hot gearbe- er iz geven der brigadir

46
00:04:37,858 --> 00:04:41,196
un mir hobn im tsugesh- tsugebundn tsu undzer, mir hobn dertseylt im,

47
00:04:41,196 --> 00:04:44,467
ver hobn ikh gehat, er hot mir hobn tsu im gehat a tsutroy epes,

48
00:04:44,490 --> 00:04:53,107
a kleynem tsutroy, un mir hobn im dertseylt az s'do bay undz a organizatsye. er zol undz helfn, mitarbetn in undzer organizatsye, mit ikh hob im ge- mir planirn aroys tsu antloyfn fun dortn.

49
00:04:54,075 --> 00:04:55,908
er hot ongenumen undzer forshlog,

50
00:04:56,050 --> 00:05:00,668
er iz arayn bay undz, Solomon Mil iz gevorn bay undz sekretar als

51
00:05:00,741 --> 00:05:06,270
mayn zim- mayn fartreter iz er gevorn, khotsh er iz geven elter fun mir mit a yor tsen, tsvelf, mistome efsher mer.

52
00:05:08,605 --> 00:05:13,239
nor in gutn frimorgn, iz gekumen tsu forn zenen gekumen tsu forn mashines,

53
00:05:13,498 --> 00:05:20,073
daytshe mashines, un m'hot geheysn zikh onlodn, mit undzere peklekh vos hobn dortn gehat dortn, ver vos hot gehat dortn mit zikh,

54
00:05:20,147 --> 00:05:25,068
m'firt undz aroys fun lager. der lager vert likvidirt un m'firt undz aroys in Sh- in Shtuthof.

55
00:05:25,935 --> 00:05:30,840
dortn tsu arbetn in di arbe- in di kontsentratsyon-lager.

56
00:05:31,825 --> 00:05:36,808
di mashinen zenen shoyn geshtanen greyt lebn lebn le- lebn Ponevezher lager,

57
00:05:36,808 --> 00:05:41,926
m'hot undz ongelodn, alemen oyf gikh, der komendant hot keyn tsayt nit gehat

58
00:05:41,950 --> 00:05:50,466
mit undz tsum reydn keyn sakh. er hot aleyn nit gevust oyf velkher oyf vos vos oyf velkher velt er iz, vayl er hot aleyn gekrogn aza min aza min prikaz az men zol undz gikh aroysfirn in Daytshland.

59
00:05:51,568 --> 00:05:57,772
eygntlekh vil ikh dermonen az nokhn krig hot mir mayner a khaver ongetrofn

60
00:05:58,909 --> 00:06:03,425
un er hot mir gezogt, herstu mir, er hot gearbet, der khaver mayner hot gearbet in K.G.B.

61
00:06:04,343 --> 00:06:09,669
un s'iz gelungen di K.G.B.istn, der khaver mayner hot geheysn Shereshnyevski,

62
00:06:09,827 --> 00:06:11,495
er iz geven a leytenant in K.G.B.

63
00:06:11,495 --> 00:06:17,635
zogt er, herstu Meyshl, zogt er, vilst zen, zogt er, dem plenik undzer, dem dem dem gevezenem komendant fun dem lager.

64
00:06:18,012 --> 00:06:20,655
mir hobn im gekhapt. un mir darfn

65
00:06:21,538 --> 00:06:29,412
onnemen, m- m'darf hobn an eydes az er iz take geven, er leyknt, er zogt, er iz nit geven keyn komendant, er iz keyn, s'shoyn geven UNK in di nokhn krig.

66
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:36,478
m'darf hobn an eydes. az du vest kenen eydes az az er iz take geven a komendant fun yidishn lager un azoy vayter.

67
00:06:36,478 --> 00:06:44,055
vayl m'darf im makhn oyf im a gerikht. darf im oder im oder im shisn, oder im vos nit iz dortn avek, araynzetsn efsher in turme.

68
00:06:44,055 --> 00:06:50,186
ikh bin mit a groysn mit groys gevilt, gezen take,

69
00:06:50,277 --> 00:06:55,316
ikh bin shoyn geven frayer mentsh, bin ikh gekumen tsu geyn in in K.G.B. un m'hot mir aroysgefirt

70
00:06:55,592 --> 00:07:00,378
dem komend- mayn mayn komendant un ikh hob im shoyn ge- ikh hob im gekent un er hot mir oykh gekent

71
00:07:00,385 --> 00:07:07,399
bay di zayendik in in in lager, in Ponevezher lager. ikh hob gegebn a kuk oyf im,

72
00:07:08,687 --> 00:07:10,790
er hot mir derkent, zogt er tsu mir,

73
00:07:11,286 --> 00:07:23,382
ya, zogt er, a dos iz der JUDE ver, mayn JUDE, ikh hob im mit marmelad ge- mit gegebn esn marmelad. zog ikh, im marmelad hostu undz gegebn esn, ober

74
00:07:23,382 --> 00:07:27,648
vifl tsayt hostu mit undz gemakht gimnastik, spetsyele gimnastik, in der fri?

75
00:07:27,908 --> 00:07:32,441
mutsh- tsu mutshenen dayne dayne mentshn? dos gedenkstu nit?

76
00:07:33,004 --> 00:07:38,263
zogt er, dos gedenk ikh nit. zog ikh, hob ikh genumen, far kaas, hob ikh im gegebn a zets ibern ponem.

77
00:07:38,337 --> 00:07:42,110
un er iz gefaln. dos iz geven mayn

78
00:07:42,167 --> 00:07:50,432
mayn eyntsiker veg vi noykem tsu noykem tsu zayn fun mayn gevezenem komendant. er hot mir oft mol andersh mol gemutshet mit ma- mit zayn gimnastik. ot er iz geven a a m-

79
00:07:50,432 --> 00:07:53,774
a a min a sh- a shvakher

80
00:07:53,774 --> 00:07:57,433
a sh- er hot gehat a shvakhkeyt tsu makhn gimnastik. spetsyele gimnastik tsu mutshen di mentshn.

81
00:07:58,857 --> 00:08:02,967
khotsh er iz ni- mit andere, antkegn di iberike,

82
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:09,451
iz er geven nit keyn nit keyn gor shlekhter vi vi di UNK mit kegn dem vos ikh hob gehat in di lagern fun Daytshland,

83
00:08:09,451 --> 00:08:12,553
di komendantn, iz er geven a goldener mentsh.

84
00:08:14,044 --> 00:08:20,636
nu, vayter vil ikh zogn az mir hot undz onge- on- ongelodn oyf di mashinen un m'hot undz gefirt in Shtuthof.

85
00:08:21,233 --> 00:08:23,606
oyfn veg hot men zikh opgeshtelt in Shualeyer lager,

86
00:08:24,895 --> 00:08:32,330
in a gevezenem lager fun fun plenikes, un m'hot undz gebrakht in Shtuthof.

87
00:08:32,573 --> 00:08:39,671
di gantse m- ven er hot undz op gefirt in shtotishe tsum Shtuthof, tsum lager fun Shtuthof, dos iz geven shpet bay nakht

88
00:08:42,028 --> 00:08:46,390
ikh hob bamerkt, zenen geshtanen dortn ongeton in shvartse shineln,

89
00:08:46,390 --> 00:08:51,478
shvartse ontsugn, di day- daytsh- daytshe fash- daytshe

90
00:08:52,873 --> 00:08:58,385
vi heysn zey dortn Geshtapistn velkhe zey hobn dortn geven di di.

91
00:09:00,923 --> 00:09:03,532
un un dem pistoletl hob ikh gehat mit zikh mitgenumen.

92
00:09:03,724 --> 00:09:06,198
ikh hob fun dest vegn gehaltn in di lantset in keshene bahaltn.

93
00:09:06,694 --> 00:09:09,877
m'hot undz gebrakht far lebn Shtuthof,

94
00:09:10,305 --> 00:09:13,303
un mir hobn m'hot undz ongezogt az m'firt undz ersht un bod.

95
00:09:13,933 --> 00:09:18,095
alemen durkh lozn durkhn bod un dortn vet men undz gebn naye zakhn,

96
00:09:18,135 --> 00:09:24,997
ontsugn mit geshtrayfte zakhn, un UNK fun dortn vet men undz, veln mir muzn geyn arbetn.

97
00:09:25,915 --> 00:09:30,600
mir zenen gelegn, undzere khevre velkhe zenen geven fun undzer fun undzer krayz,

98
00:09:30,758 --> 00:09:35,825
azoy tsu zogn di untererdler, un mir hobn ge- ikh getrakht vos ken men do itster ton?

99
00:09:35,825 --> 00:09:38,952
zog ikh tsu zey, vos zol men ton mitn mitn revolver?

100
00:09:39,330 --> 00:09:43,391
oyber m'unterzukht dortn, un m'darf nokh geyn durkhn bod, m'vet undz oyston, vet men dokh gefinen.

101
00:09:44,562 --> 00:09:52,537
nu, mir hobn bashlosn dem revolver hob ikh bashlosn oystsugrobn a grub un ikh hob im azoy fargrobn lebn Shtuthofer lager in a in in zamd.

102
00:09:55,851 --> 00:09:58,308
ye in Shtuthof hob ikh hob ikh getrofn mayn foter.

103
00:09:58,804 --> 00:10:01,025
getrofn mayn foter un mayn bruderl.

104
00:10:05,706 --> 00:10:10,492
zayendik in Shtuthof etlekhe teg, hot men hob ikh shoyn hobn mir glaykh bamerkt az s'iz

105
00:10:10,617 --> 00:10:16,596
az men az do der lager iz nit tsu arbetn, nor der lager iz spetsyel tsu

106
00:10:16,596 --> 00:10:22,913
brengen tsum toyt di yidn velkhe m'brengen velkhe bre- velkhe men hot gebrakht tsu zey. men hot undz arayngetribn in di barakn glaykh,

107
00:10:24,066 --> 00:10:25,607
mir zenen durkhgegangen tsu ersht dem bod,

108
00:10:25,607 --> 00:10:31,805
un shpeter hot men hot undz arayngetribn mit di mit di shoyn di naye bgodim, mit di shtrayflingen in di barakn,

109
00:10:32,402 --> 00:10:34,387
oyf di nares hot men undz avekgeleygt,

110
00:10:35,507 --> 00:10:38,589
un yedn in der fri flegt men undz oyfva- oyfheybn

111
00:10:39,456 --> 00:10:45,435
tsu geyn tsu avekshteln oyfn oysshteln oyfn plats, oystsutseyln, arunternemen,

112
00:10:45,435 --> 00:10:52,274
der der di kapos velkhe hobn mit undz ongefirt zenen geven poylisher, poylishe poylishe banditn,

113
00:10:53,142 --> 00:10:57,726
velkhe hobn zikh ge- velkhe hobn gemutshet spetsyel, m'hot zey avekgeshtelt spetsyel tsu mutshen di yidn.

114
00:10:58,204 --> 00:11:03,463
ikh gedenk di in der fri flegt men ven er flegt undz aroystraybn fun di barakn, flegt men zikh darfn avekshteln oyfn plats,

115
00:11:03,553 --> 00:11:07,715
flegt er flegt er shrayen, "MUTZEN AUF un MUTZEN op."

116
00:11:07,992 --> 00:11:12,677
in dem moment flegt men muzn arunternemen di hitlen, un a gebn a klap ibern der erd.

117
00:11:14,117 --> 00:11:18,062
es zol zayn alts in eyn in eyn in eyn in eyn otem gemakht.

118
00:11:18,062 --> 00:11:24,421
ale di gantse rey yidn velkhe zenen geshtanen in di reyen un hot dos gemu- -mu- -muzt makhn in eyn moment, es zol zikh derhern di klap fun di hitlen.

119
00:11:24,664 --> 00:11:27,122
un der un un er flegt shrayen, "nu MUTZEN!

120
00:11:27,853 --> 00:11:31,706
AUF!" dos heyst, flegt men darfn nemen di hitlen un arop gibn aroyfleygn oyfn kop.

121
00:11:31,706 --> 00:11:34,648
un ver es flegt nit kenen onhaltn dem dem shvung fun dem,

122
00:11:35,059 --> 00:11:38,377
flegt tsuloyfn der kapo un gut tseklapn ibern ponem.

123
00:11:40,375 --> 00:11:43,221
un nu mir zenen shoyn geven tsugevoynt tsugevoynt tsu azelkhene zakhn.

124
00:11:45,117 --> 00:11:55,711
m'hot undz oft mol, nit eyn klap hob ikh gekrogn far far dem vos ikh hob nit vos mir hobn nit gekent araynloyfn arayn- arayngeyn in barak vayl in barak di tir fun barak fun barak hot geven zeyer a shmole,

125
00:11:55,711 --> 00:11:59,088
un di kapos flegn undz traybn dortn in barak,

126
00:11:59,088 --> 00:12:03,238
alemen tsuzamen unter di kleyne tirl. farshteyt zikh durkh a kleyne tirl iz shver arayntsugeyn,

127
00:12:03,238 --> 00:12:06,863
flegt men zikh shtupn eyner dem tsveytn, ver s'flegt nit bavayzn arayntsugeyn durkhn tir

128
00:12:06,863 --> 00:12:12,364
flegt men flegt sh- flegn shteyn di di kapos, di poylishe kapos, un klapn ibern ibern nakn ibern kop.

129
00:12:15,593 --> 00:12:18,337
etlekhe teg zenen mir geven in K. in in Shtuthof.

130
00:12:18,613 --> 00:12:22,778
shpeter hot men undz ongehoybn o- o -m'hot undz oysgemushtirt un m'hot gezogt

131
00:12:22,778 --> 00:12:25,830
di daytshn hobn gezogt az m'firt undz aroys in di arbets-lager in der hal.

132
00:12:27,928 --> 00:12:32,825
dem mitn foter hob ikh bashlosn,

133
00:12:32,920 --> 00:12:38,345
un der bruderl mayner iz geven, ober der foter mitn bruderl hot men aroysgefirt fun geto in UNK.

134
00:12:38,345 --> 00:12:45,795
der ikh hob bashlosn, mir hobn beyde bashlosn, az efsher zoln mir fo- mayn bruderl iz geven zeyer a shvakher in gezunt,

135
00:12:45,795 --> 00:12:48,374
un mir hobn bashlosn iz der bruder vet efsher blaybn

136
00:12:48,499 --> 00:12:54,495
in nu er er zol zikh tsu tsu tsu onshlisn on di kinder.

137
00:12:54,495 --> 00:12:59,597
tsu efsher vet men di kinder nit tshepenen. mir hobn keyn fal nit keyn fal nit gegleybt az di daytshn zenen oyf azoy fil

138
00:12:59,991 --> 00:13:09,775
az zey zoln nemen kinder un zey um- un zey umbrengen. efsher veln di ki- veln di kinder efsher blaybn lebn. hobn mir bashlosn az der bruderl zol geyn tsvishn di kinder, un mir mitn foter velkhe zenen shoyn geven mer veyniker shtarker,

139
00:13:09,775 --> 00:13:12,269
veln geyn frayvilik zikh ot araynzetsn in di vagonen

140
00:13:12,546 --> 00:13:18,092
un fi- un geyn, f- lozn zikh firn in ar- in di arbets-lagern, in di konts-lagern,

141
00:13:18,165 --> 00:13:20,218
fun Daytshland. azoy iz geven.

142
00:13:20,832 --> 00:13:22,952
dem kin- dem bruderl hobn mir gelozn,

143
00:13:22,958 --> 00:13:26,428
ikh hob zikh dervust durkhn durkhn bruderl az er

144
00:13:26,670 --> 00:13:30,241
az er hot gezen di mame durkhn sh- durkh dem shtekhldrot,

145
00:13:30,687 --> 00:13:36,148
az di mame iz oykh geven bazunders bazunders opgeteylt fun di fun ale i- fun di iberike froyen,

146
00:13:38,702 --> 00:13:43,095
un m'hot geredt vegn dem az di kinder mit di m- mit di mit di froyen veln zayn tsuzamen.

147
00:13:43,095 --> 00:13:46,189
m'vet zey UNK nit tshepenen dervayle.

148
00:13:46,819 --> 00:13:51,065
zenen mir shoyn geven tsufridn vegn dem az der bruder vet kho- vet khotsh zayn mit di mamen tsuzamen.

149
00:13:51,814 --> 00:13:55,925
ikh bin oykh tsugegangen tsum drot, ikh hob derzen mayn mamen, ikh hob zikh mit ir gezegnt dem letstn mol,

150
00:13:58,615 --> 00:14:08,581
un mir zenen avekgeforn, m'hot undz gefirt in di arbets-lagern fun Dakhau fun Dakhau.

151
00:14:09,313 --> 00:14:15,537
farshteyt zikh oyfn veg hot men undz keyn esn nit gegebn. mir zenen geven ale bavak, m'hot undz lang gefirt, etlekhe teg hot men undz gefirt, mir zenen gevorn ale bavaksn.

152
00:14:15,537 --> 00:14:24,124
mir zenen ge- keyn esn hungerik, in vagones fun fi vag- in fi vagones, ongeshtopte mit mentshn,

153
00:14:24,518 --> 00:14:30,131
biz m'hot undz gebrakht in Dakhau, s'heyst in in a in a shtetl Landsberg lebn Dakhau.

154
00:14:30,323 --> 00:14:38,957
dortn hot men undz arayngeshpart in a lager lager numer tsvey. mir mitn foter.

155
00:14:40,752 --> 00:14:46,229
nu in dem lager in dortn tsvey, hobn mir derzen glaykh dershpirt glaykh di ershte tsores.

156
00:14:48,075 --> 00:14:51,899
mir hobn dortn oykh gelebt in erd-barakn farsheydene, erd-barakn oyf nares,

157
00:14:53,492 --> 00:14:55,477
m'flegt undz traybn in der fri tsu der arbet,

158
00:14:55,602 --> 00:15:01,032
gor in der fri flegt men undz ersht oystseyln oyfn apel, oystseyln verer vifl zenen do mentshn.

159
00:15:01,032 --> 00:15:05,090
vifl zenen do asirim azoy tsu zogn, vifl zenen do, tsi keyn eyner felt nit.

160
00:15:05,090 --> 00:15:09,805
oyb es flegt flegn feln ver nit iz eyner oyfn loytn tsol, flegt der komendant

161
00:15:09,996 --> 00:15:13,365
glaykh loyfn iber di barakn zukhn im di mentshn un

162
00:15:13,540 --> 00:15:17,871
oyb m'hot dir nor gefunen flegt er flegt er lebediker shoyn fun im nit aroysgeyn fun zayne hent.

163
00:15:19,243 --> 00:15:22,258
s'shoyn geven osyen tsayt, kalt,

164
00:15:24,306 --> 00:15:31,809
ikh vil dertseyln eynem a eynem a epizod velkhe m'k- velkhe ikh ken im vegn im nit fargesn. UNK.

165
00:15:33,216 --> 00:15:43,824
lager tsvey hot men undz hobn undz gegebn zeyer shlekht esn farshteyt zikh. mir hobn glaykh dershpirt az mir veln do lang nit oyshaltn.

166
00:15:43,898 --> 00:15:48,296
a fakt iz geven az m'hot gebrakht dortn in dem lager finf hundert yidn fun Tshekhoslovakye, fun Prag,

167
00:15:48,353 --> 00:15:50,001
inteligente mentshn azelkhe.

168
00:15:50,766 --> 00:15:55,985
zey hobn in a kurtser tsayt arum iz fun zey keyn eyner nit geblibn keyn lebediker.

169
00:15:55,985 --> 00:15:59,467
vayl zey hobn nit gekent oyshaltn di sh- di di di badingungen fun dem lager.

170
00:16:00,199 --> 00:16:05,863
m'hot zey ge- zenen ale finf tsu finf hundert man zenen geven oysgeshtorbn ale in a k- in a kurtse tsayt.

171
00:16:06,088 --> 00:16:07,871
keyner hot iz fun zey nit geblibn lebn.

172
00:16:08,063 --> 00:16:15,819
ober di litvishe yidn velkhe zenen shoyn geven a bisl ayngevoynt fun di lager badingungen zayendik shoyn in di getos mit di un farshidene dortn a- andere lagern,

173
00:16:15,825 --> 00:16:21,253
zenen shoyn ayngevoynt tsu tsu dem hunger un tsu dem noyt, un m'hot durkhgemakht fun dest vegn.

174
00:16:21,597 --> 00:16:26,635
nu ikh zog nit az zey zenen geblibn ale lebn, nor nor a klenere tsol fun zey flegn oysshtarbn.

175
00:16:28,363 --> 00:16:30,449
fun lager tsvey hot men undz aribergefirt in lager elf.

176
00:16:31,418 --> 00:16:33,186
dos iz geven a geshreklikher lager.

177
00:16:33,186 --> 00:16:40,046
dos iz geven a lager fun an arbets-lager vu men hot getribn in der fri di arbeter

178
00:16:40,046 --> 00:16:42,451
bay tsen bay fuftsn kilometer tsu fus,

179
00:16:42,451 --> 00:16:47,544
in di grubn vu m'hot geboyt kentik dortn di V.

180
00:16:48,090 --> 00:16:52,280
di V. daytshishe V. eroplanen di letste. dortn hot men genumen

181
00:16:52,280 --> 00:17:01,575
yidn un m'hot oyf di oyf tsu boyen mit tsement mit beton fun betonirn dortn di un- di un- di un- di untererdishe

182
00:17:01,630 --> 00:17:10,460
di untererdishe azelkhene UNK un dortn hot men ge- hot men hot men gedarft arbetn unter a shtrenge vakh.

183
00:17:12,053 --> 00:17:21,801
ikh muz aykh dertseyln vegn dem vi azoy ikh bin ikh bin gegangen tsu der arbet dortn yedn tog,

184
00:17:22,954 --> 00:17:28,246
vos heyst gegangen? m'hot undz getribn tsu der arbet yedn tog. gegesn gegesn hot men undz gegebn zeyer shvakh, zeyer veynik,

185
00:17:28,995 --> 00:17:30,857
un geven hungerik un oysgemutshet,

186
00:17:30,857 --> 00:17:37,016
un ikh hob bash- ikh hob der- dersh- der- geyendik farbay geyendik tsu der ar- tsu der arbet, hob ikh bamerkt az s'do a feld

187
00:17:37,016 --> 00:17:43,080
bamerkt a feld fun kartofl. vos iz ge- vos dortn hobn opgevaksn kartofl.

188
00:17:44,250 --> 00:17:47,855
hob ikh bashlosn zikh aroys tsu ganvenen funem arbets-ort ibern parkan,

189
00:17:49,262 --> 00:17:58,166
in mitn der arbet az der postn zol mir nit bamerkn, un ikh zol efsher kenen on- on grablen a bisl kartofl un arayntsuleygn zikh bay zikh un arayntrogn in lager arayn.

190
00:18:00,518 --> 00:18:04,950
ikh hob fun dem feld fun di kartofl fun dest vegn gefunen,

191
00:18:05,175 --> 00:18:09,860
un ikh hob ongehoybn grablen untern shney, nor di- dine shikhtn shney, un ikh hob ongehoybn ganvenen di kartofl

192
00:18:10,002 --> 00:18:12,402
un geven zeyer tsufridn vos ikh zol kenen

193
00:18:12,402 --> 00:18:17,977
mit di kartoflekh efsher helfn zikh un dem f- mayn foter iz oykh geven in dem zelbn lager, khotsh helfn im, er iz gelegn krank.

194
00:18:17,977 --> 00:18:22,802
un ikh hob im gevolt khotshik oysbrengen etlekhe kartofl tsum shtiln zayn hunger.

195
00:18:23,653 --> 00:18:28,797
ikh hob zikh arayngeton in der a- in in dem grablen, az ikh hob fargesn di tsayt,

196
00:18:28,797 --> 00:18:31,329
un in der zelber tsayt iz der arbets-brigade,

197
00:18:31,329 --> 00:18:33,823
s'hot zikh geendikt der arbets- di tsayt fun der arbets-brigade,

198
00:18:33,897 --> 00:18:37,367
un zey ze- m'hot zey avekgetribn tsurik in lager un ikh bin geblibn eyner aleyn.

199
00:18:37,390 --> 00:18:39,679
ikh kum tsu geyn oyfn arbets-ort, keyner iz nito.

200
00:18:39,887 --> 00:18:41,400
ikh trakht zikh, vos zol ikh do ton?

201
00:18:43,144 --> 00:18:47,862
in der zelber tsayt hot men shoyn oysgetseylt in arbets-lager az s'felt eyn mentsh.

202
00:18:48,814 --> 00:18:54,916
hot men aroysgelozn di postns mit hint tsum zukhn dem mentshn. der mentsh bin geven UNK bin mir geven.

203
00:18:57,252 --> 00:18:58,657
s'shoyn geven shpet,

204
00:18:58,657 --> 00:19:04,226
un ikh hob farlorn di oryentatsye vu der lager gefint zikh, ikh hob ongehoybn tsu blondzhenen. ikh hob gevolt kumen shoyn aleyn in lager dokh vi nit iz,

205
00:19:04,226 --> 00:19:11,403
vayl ikh hob farshtanen az m- az s'vet feln a mentsh veln mir shpeter vet men shpeter kenen derfar laydn di iberike oykh fun lager.

206
00:19:12,321 --> 00:19:16,123
hob ikh genumen hob ikh ongehoybn blondzhenen, un ikh hob derhert

207
00:19:16,123 --> 00:19:24,299
es biln hint geferlekh, di m'hot aroysgef- aroysgekukt postns mit hint zukhn, mit shpir-hint zukhn dem ge- antlofenem mentshn.

208
00:19:24,299 --> 00:19:27,215
un zey hobn mir gekhapt. zey farshteyt zikh mir glaykh gekhapt.

209
00:19:27,323 --> 00:19:33,713
zey hobn mikh gekhapt, un avekge- tsu ersht hobn zey mir gut ongeshlogn, gegebn, gekrogn fun zey ge- gu- gute klep,

210
00:19:34,123 --> 00:19:38,998
nor eyn daytsh velkher iz geven dortn der sh- der der eltster fun zey hot nit gelozt hargenen mir.

211
00:19:38,998 --> 00:19:41,473
zogt er tsu mir, zogt er tsu zey tsu zey,

212
00:19:41,473 --> 00:19:44,898
ikh vel zikh mit zey mit im, zogt er, aleyn oprekhenen. tshepet im nit.

213
00:19:45,042 --> 00:19:47,280
un tsu mir zogt er oyf daytsh, zogt er,

214
00:19:47,775 --> 00:19:54,873
"veyst, du kleyner yunger, ikh men ikh vel dikh LA- LASSEN SCHLAGEN dikh."

215
00:19:55,234 --> 00:19:59,075
du gey foroys, un m'hot mir gefirt in lager, un er hot mir nit gelozn shlogn.

216
00:19:59,908 --> 00:20:05,212
ven ven m- ven m'iz gekumen in lager tsuzamen mit di gantse kompanye postns velkhe zenen gegangen hinter mir mit di hint,

217
00:20:05,212 --> 00:20:07,006
m'hot mir arayngefirt tsum komendant.

218
00:20:07,620 --> 00:20:11,996
der komendant fun lager iz geven a vilder mentsh a geferlekher,

219
00:20:11,996 --> 00:20:16,307
er hot shoyn gevust zayne f- vi azoy tsu mutshenen mentshn.

220
00:20:16,307 --> 00:20:21,536
hot er bashlosn oystsufirn oyf mir a ekzekutsye. mir oyfhengen oyf a drot.

221
00:20:22,504 --> 00:20:24,152
ikh zol blaybn hengen oyf a drot.

222
00:20:26,925 --> 00:20:31,272
er hot genumen nokh tsvey mentshn lebn zikh, tsvey postns,

223
00:20:31,313 --> 00:20:34,513
farbundn m- ge- tsugefirt mir tsum shtolp,

224
00:20:34,671 --> 00:20:38,647
aroyfgetsoygn a drot oyfn shtolp in der heykh, farbundn mir di hent oyf hintn,

225
00:20:38,856 --> 00:20:43,561
dos iz geven a eyne fun di greste g- greste mutshenish in di lagern fun fun OSWIECIM.

226
00:20:43,561 --> 00:20:49,838
er iz kentik geven dortn komendant in OSWIECIM, un er hot gevust di ale farsheydene metodn vi tsu m- oys- oystsumatern mentshn.

227
00:20:49,838 --> 00:20:55,928
hot men farbundn di hent oyf hintn mit di drotn, un hot men mir tsugebundn dem drot un mir aroyfgetsoygn oyfn shtolp in der heykh.

228
00:20:56,524 --> 00:21:02,326
ikh bin gehangen do oyf shtolp farshteyt zikh ikh gedenk shoyn nit vifl tsayt.

229
00:21:02,326 --> 00:21:08,331
nor ikh veys nor eyns, az di kartofl velkhe ikh hob gehat bahaltn hobn zikh aroysgeshotn bay mir.

230
00:21:09,298 --> 00:21:14,928
hot der komendant bamerkt, zogt er, "o! du host nokh kartofl mit zikh? dan muztu hengen nokh mer!

231
00:21:15,694 --> 00:21:19,063
ikh bin gehangen a kurtse tsayt, biz ikh hob farlorn dem bavustzayn.

232
00:21:19,677 --> 00:21:21,842
ikh gedenk nit ver vi azoy es pasirt,

233
00:21:21,842 --> 00:21:27,298
nor ikh veys nor az ver nit iz opgesh- opgeshnitn dem drot, ver nit iz nor biz haynt veys ikh nit.

234
00:21:27,473 --> 00:21:32,174
un m'hot mir arayngetrogn in barak. in barak un m'hot mir avekgeleygt oyfn nare.

235
00:21:32,265 --> 00:21:36,210
di hent zenen bay mir geven tseshnitn fun di drotn, farblutikt geferlekh.

236
00:21:36,210 --> 00:21:39,231
di harts ligndik di harts bay mir geven

237
00:21:39,231 --> 00:21:48,054
geferlekhe veytogn un di oygn bay mir geven un di kop hot mir ge- ge- geshvindlt, ikh hob nit gevust oyf velkhe velt ikh bin. un m'hot mir avekgeleygt dortn in in barak lign.

238
00:21:50,220 --> 00:21:54,858
undzer blok-eltster iz geven a yid. er hot geheysn Itsik Mayer.

239
00:21:54,858 --> 00:22:00,086
er iz geven a yid mit a groysn bagazh.

240
00:22:00,328 --> 00:22:02,752
er iz geven di lagern fun OSWIECIM.

241
00:22:04,767 --> 00:22:08,062
un er flegt, er hot zikh dortn oysgelernt vi azoy tsum

242
00:22:08,062 --> 00:22:15,256
vi azoy tsum shlogn di yidn. er iz geven a zeyer a biterer mentsh. a Lodzher yid, a Lod- fun Lodzh, a Varshe- a poylisher yid.

243
00:22:15,702 --> 00:22:17,833
Itsik Mayer hot men im dort hot men im gerufn.

244
00:22:17,833 --> 00:22:23,052
oyf yidish heyst er Itsik Meyer, nor azoy mitn mitn aktsen fun di poylisher heyst er "Mayer".

245
00:22:23,802 --> 00:22:26,709
fun dest vegn iz li- li- ligndik in barak,

246
00:22:26,709 --> 00:22:30,346
hot er eyn mol tsu mir tsuget- a farvundeter in barak, hot er tsu mir tsugetrogn

247
00:22:30,346 --> 00:22:34,834
a sh- a gedikhte kesele mit mit z- mit zup, mit gedikhte zup.

248
00:22:34,834 --> 00:22:36,800
un er hot tsu mir gezogt, di verter gedenk ikh,

249
00:22:36,800 --> 00:22:43,750
"ey du, pshakrev! du nem nu balek fun di deyshke

250
00:22:43,750 --> 00:22:49,225
un makh zikh nit visndik du du bist bay mir a held!

251
00:22:49,570 --> 00:22:52,821
a rikh in dayn totn's totn's totn's arayn."

252
00:22:54,025 --> 00:22:55,622
ot di verter gedenk ikh zayne.

253
00:22:56,134 --> 00:23:00,735
un a tsveytn mol hot er mir oykh tsugetro- oyf morgn hot er mir oykh tsugetrogn di bisele a bisl gedikhte zup.

254
00:23:02,867 --> 00:23:09,515
di iberike hot er, di iberike yidn velkhe zenen geven in barak, hot er mit mi- tsu zey batsoygn zikh zeyer nit gut.

255
00:23:09,515 --> 00:23:14,589
tsu mir hot er gehat kentik rakhmones un er hot mir geholfn blaybn lebn.

256
00:23:16,519 --> 00:23:19,787
a lange tsayt bin ikh gelegn in barak a farvundeter,

257
00:23:20,350 --> 00:23:29,676
un ikh hob farshtanen az ikh muz blaybn lebn. als eyns ikh bin nokh yung un ikh muz, ikh lo- ikh ikh hob gehoft az ikh volt vern bafrayt.

258
00:23:30,643 --> 00:23:34,063
tsu arbet hot men nit geshikt vayl ikh bin geven in gantsn farvundet.

259
00:23:35,605 --> 00:23:38,046
nor bislekhvayz hob ikh zikh avekgeshtelt oyf di fis,

260
00:23:38,085 --> 00:23:41,909
un ikh bin shoyn aroys di ershte tsayt tsu der arbet.

261
00:23:44,717 --> 00:23:53,402
nu vayter, in der tsayt iz geven, s'shoyn geven friling tsayt

262
00:23:54,117 --> 00:23:57,013
finf un fertsikstn yor, dos iz shoyn geven MART monat dakht zikh.

263
00:23:57,643 --> 00:24:02,171
di yidn di asirim fun fun lager hobn ongehoybn kran- krenken oyf oyf tifus.

264
00:24:02,171 --> 00:24:06,733
fun fun fun hunger, fun kelt, fun noyt.

265
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:10,985
ikh bin arumgelofn, ikh bin ikh bin geven oykh hungerik vi ale,

266
00:24:11,346 --> 00:24:16,329
ikh bin shoyn geven enlekh tsu a musulman. a musulman dos iz a mentsh velkher er farlirt dem gantsn oyszen zaynem,

267
00:24:16,329 --> 00:24:19,052
er vert es es es zeen zikh bay im aroys di beyner,

268
00:24:19,665 --> 00:24:23,155
un un mer nit vi di di di beyner fun di fun di shokes UNK,

269
00:24:23,155 --> 00:24:25,906
s'iz di velkhe zenen geven in lager veysn velkher heyst a musulman.

270
00:24:25,906 --> 00:24:30,775
afile in di sovetishe lagern veysn oykh vos heyst a musulman. ikh hob nit lang geredt mit a mentshn, zogt er,

271
00:24:30,784 --> 00:24:34,709
er hot ibergezetst mayne mayne memuarn vegn vegn dem, zogt er, o

272
00:24:34,709 --> 00:24:40,095
di shraybst in dayne memuarn vegn musulman, zogt er, ikh veys vos dos heyst, zogt er, in Sibir hobn mir es oykh gehat azelkhene musulmanen.

273
00:24:40,489 --> 00:24:42,575
aza min bin ikh geven oykh shoyn gevorn.

274
00:24:43,459 --> 00:24:47,891
nor plutsung, ya, geyendik azoy bay di barakn hob ikh

275
00:24:48,049 --> 00:24:53,859
gezukht vu tsu a shtik- khapn a shtikl broyt oder a shtikl kartofl, kedey tsu shtiln shtiln dem hunger.

276
00:24:53,859 --> 00:24:59,546
un mertsn teyl hob hob ikh zikh bin bin ikh arayn in di zone vu es zenen gelegn di tifus kranke.

277
00:24:59,546 --> 00:25:03,028
vayl dortn flegn di kranke shoyn, a sakh kranke flegn farn shtarbn

278
00:25:03,051 --> 00:25:06,043
flegn zey iberlozn di shtikele broyt vos zeyer portsye broyt,

279
00:25:06,043 --> 00:25:10,875
un fun zey hob ikh getrakht efsher, hob ikh ge- gevelt vos nit far zikh vos nit iz gefinen.

280
00:25:11,877 --> 00:25:17,912
ikh efn di tir fun a barak, ikh gib a kuk unter a koldre, es ligt a bavaksener mentsh

281
00:25:18,087 --> 00:25:20,983
aza min, ober mit azelkhene shey- sheyne gute oygn.

282
00:25:21,377 --> 00:25:25,415
ikh gib a kuk, epes a bakanter, ver iz er?

283
00:25:25,415 --> 00:25:29,136
ikh hob es dermont. dos iz mayn amoliker lerer Yisroel Kaplan.

284
00:25:29,136 --> 00:25:35,090
ikh hob im dakht zikh vegn dem dermont, er iz geven mayn ershter lerer in Slabodke.

285
00:25:38,151 --> 00:25:46,852
er hot mir derzen, zogt er, o Gegele! er hot mir gerufn, in der tsayt fun lernen hot er hob ikh gehat a tsunomen Gegele, loyt der familye Geguzhinski.

286
00:25:47,702 --> 00:25:50,261
Gegele, zogt er, bist do, zogt er, bist mayner a shiler!

287
00:25:50,402 --> 00:25:53,403
her tsu, efsher kenstu mir ton a toyve?

288
00:25:53,403 --> 00:25:55,374
zog mir, efsher kenstu mir brengen

289
00:25:55,431 --> 00:26:01,460
a pa- shtikl papir vayse. ot, zogt er, ikh kentik kentik gey ikh shoyn nit oyshaltn, zogt er, vayle zest dokh vi ikh lig oyf tifus krank.

290
00:26:01,460 --> 00:26:05,634
ikh vel shoyn mistome shtarbn, ober farn toyt vil ikh onshraybn khotshabe vegn mayn lebn.

291
00:26:05,725 --> 00:26:07,018
ikh hob nit oyf vos.

292
00:26:08,307 --> 00:26:14,859
un a shtik papir iz geven shver tsu krign in lager. nor fun dest vegn bin ikh aroysgelofn fun fun zayn barak un ikh hob gezukht ikh hob gefunen a shtikl

293
00:26:14,859 --> 00:26:17,227
tsekneytshte papir un ikh hob im gegebn.

294
00:26:17,790 --> 00:26:22,610
un azoy hot der der lerer Kaplan geshribn vegn zayn lebn in lager.

295
00:26:23,089 --> 00:26:25,592
tsvishn andere vil ikh zogn az ersht nokhn krig,

296
00:26:25,592 --> 00:26:28,686
tsufelik hob ikh geleyent a tsaytung, in der Yerusholaim Belite,

297
00:26:28,776 --> 00:26:33,326
az s'gevorn nayntsik yor eynem a Yisroel Kaplan. nayntsik yor iz im gevorn.

298
00:26:34,108 --> 00:26:36,856
m'hot im bagrist. un mit aza mit zayn fotografye.

299
00:26:36,856 --> 00:26:44,492
ikh hob gegebn a kuk di fotografye, ikh geb a kuk, s'rikhtik s'mayn lerer. vi azoy iz er geblibn lebn? ikh hob zikh nit forgeshtelt az a mentsh velkher iz gelegn shoyn oyfn toytn bet

300
00:26:44,492 --> 00:26:48,109
hot zikh hot nokh derlebt biz nayntsik yor, er lebt in Yisroel.

301
00:26:49,110 --> 00:26:50,892
un ikh hob gikh avekgeshikt a telegrame

302
00:26:51,895 --> 00:26:55,297
tsu im un ikh hob im bagrist mit zayn nayntsik yorikn iberley.

303
00:26:56,299 --> 00:26:57,899
hob ikh glaykh tsurik gekrogn a briv,

304
00:26:57,899 --> 00:27:00,312
mayn liber talmed, shraybt er tsu mir,

305
00:27:00,312 --> 00:27:03,974
mir freyt zeyer vu du lebst un ikh vil dir zen. kum tsu forn.

